text: Bangalaia camerunica is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1974. It is known from Cameroon.BioLib.cz - Bangalaia camerunica. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Prosopocerini Category:Beetles described in 1974
